                    </marginalia_text>
                    <person name="Archimedes"/>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>The geometrical industry of Archmedes, and the technical torture tools, equally terrifying and wonderful.
            </translation>
        </marginalia>
        
        <marginalia hand="Italian">
            <language ident="LA">
                <position book_orientation="0" place="head">
                    <marginalia_text>
                        Vnus artifex instar mille bellatorum: nec mille bellatores instar vnius artificis. 
                        Tanti valet peritissima Mechanica, in primisq[ue] Mechanopoetica.
                    </marginalia_text>
                </position>
            </language>
            <translation>One craftsman is equal to a thousand fighters, and a thousand fighters are not up to one single craftsman. 
                So much more superior is the very clever art of engineering, especially mechanical engineering.
            </translation>
        </marginalia>
        
